character.name: Physical Appearance: Young girl, approximately 8-10 years old, with long, flowing blonde hair that reaches past her shoulders with natural waves. Fair complexion with delicate facial features. Slender, athletic build appropriate for her age, showing the flexibility and grace of a martial artist in training. Outfit & Attire: Wearing a traditional white taekwondo dobok (uniform) consisting of a white wrap-style gi top with long sleeves and loose-fitting white martial arts pants. Yellow belt tied around her waist, signifying her beginner-to-intermediate rank in taekwondo. Training barefoot, as is traditional in the martial art.
